This is a mix of old vanity generator files.
The new files are vangen.cpp and vangen.h


build:
make vangen

if you get: fatal error: pcre.h: No such file or directory
sudo apt-get install libpcre++-dev

if you get: fatal error: openssl/sha.h: No such file or directory
sudo apt-get install libssl-dev



usage:
./vangen spb Spider

help:
./vangen help
./vangen help name


